rows.label: bf07280100_0010
rows.name: [ML:undisp]

rows.label: bf07280100_0020
rows.name: My lady?

rows.label: bf07280100_0030
rows.name:
For the last time, I'm fine.
Why don't you just worry about yourself?

rows.label: bf07280100_0040
rows.name: But-

rows.label: bf07280100_0042
rows.name:
You gotta admire Shellhead over there.
He just put it right out there.

rows.label: bf07280100_0044
rows.name: [ML:undisp ]Hmm?

rows.label: bf07280100_0046
rows.name: And here I am...

rows.label: bf07280100_0048
rows.name: Byakko.

rows.label: bf07280100_0050
rows.name:
I'm gonna put myself to the test.
Right here. I've decided.

rows.label: bf07280100_0055
rows.name: My lady-

rows.label: bf07280100_0060
rows.name: Very well.

rows.label: bf07280100_0070
rows.name:
This mist is thick. Makes me feel like I'm
swimming through the Cloud Sea.

rows.label: bf07280100_0080
rows.name:
This mist is produced when a fossilized Divine Beast body
reacts with the atmosphere.

rows.label: bf07280100_0090
rows.name: It's why it's so hard to breathe down here.

rows.label: bf07280100_0100
rows.name: [ML:undisp]

rows.label: bf07280100_0110
rows.name: Nia?

rows.label: bf07280100_0120
rows.name: What now?

rows.label: bf07280100_0130
rows.name: Are you in pain?

rows.label: bf07280100_0140
rows.name: I'm strugglin' to breathe like everyone else.

rows.label: bf07280100_0150
rows.name: And I'm a little dizzy, that's all.

rows.label: bf07280100_0160
rows.name: Oh right...

rows.label: bf07280100_0170
rows.name:
When that happens, it's best to just try and
empty your head of all thoughts.

rows.label: bf07280100_0180
rows.name: What?

rows.label: bf07280100_0190
rows.name: It's an old salvager trick.

rows.label: bf07280100_0200
rows.name:
When you swim down deep, it feels like your
head's gonna implode.

rows.label: bf07280100_0210
rows.name:
You just go with it, don't fight it.
Then you stop noticing the pressure.

rows.label: bf07280100_0220
rows.name: Why not give it a go?

rows.label: bf07280100_0230
rows.name: Empty my head, eh?

rows.label: bf07280100_0240
rows.name:
You mean I have to start acting as
daft as you?

rows.label: bf07280100_0250
rows.name: Tall order.

rows.label: bf07280100_0260
rows.name: Hey, that's not very nice!

rows.label: bf07280100_0270
rows.name: Everyone! Over here!

rows.label: bf07280100_0280
rows.name: Tora think this way lead down.

rows.label: bf07280100_0290
rows.name: It certainly doesn't look like a natural formation.

rows.label: bf07280100_0300
rows.name: Maybe it was grave robbers?

rows.label: bf07280100_0310
rows.name:
There's not too much worth stealing round here.
Well, apart from...

rows.label: bf07280100_0320
rows.name: Whatever it was that Adel hid down here.

rows.label: bf07280100_0330
rows.name: Just a guess.

rows.label: bf07280100_0340
rows.name:
It's possible that Shin and his accomplices
have been here.

rows.label: bf07280100_0350
rows.name:
Then...they found out about the sunken ship,
and went to Avaritia.

rows.label: bf07280100_0360
rows.name: Still just a guess, but a pretty good one.

rows.label: bf07280100_0370
rows.name:
Then there won't be anything left
to find, will there? Sheesh.

rows.label: bf07280100_0380
rows.name:
Well, if that was the case then you'd expect them to
already have the third sword.

rows.label: bf07280100_0390
rows.name: But they clearly don't have it.

rows.label: bf07280100_0400
rows.name:
No, I do not think Adel would let
the sword be so easily found.

rows.label: bf07280100_0410
rows.name:
No point in worrying.
Let's just press on!
